{"tid":807944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【飛燕襲日】關西京都神社寺廟重創　最少15處文物被毀","createTime":"2018-09-06T02:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T18:21:59.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c229071455072576efcb7aedd27c97c5dcaa1c42","tid":807944,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/temple-05_QgkRR_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftemple-05_QgkRR_1200x0.png&h=a7d4ba01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：twitter圖片、新聞片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n颱風飛燕吹襲關西，京都多處列為世界文化遺產的寺廟神社亦被重創。京都北區賞櫻勝地平野神社的拜殿，在強風中倒塌，亦有櫻花樹被風吹倒；遊覽京都幾乎必到的二條城，國寶二之丸御殿屋頂瓦片脫落，菊花皇徽亦受損。鄰近京都站的世界遺產西本願寺內的南能舞場牆面倒塌，這些名勝目前暫停開放參觀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hiranojinja/status/1036948579489730562?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1036948579489730562&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E9%25A3%259B%25E7%2587%2595%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E9%2597%259C%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E9%2583%25BD%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25AF%25BA%25E5%25BB%259F%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2589%25B5-%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25B0%259115%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%2589%25A9%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2580%2F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhiranojinja%2Fstatus%2F1036948579489730562%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1036948579489730562%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fthestandnews.com%252Finternational%252F%2525E9%2525A3%25259B%2525E7%252587%252595%2525E8%2525A5%2525B2%2525E6%252597%2525A5-%2525E9%252597%25259C%2525E8%2525A5%2525BF%2525E4%2525BA%2525AC%2525E9%252583%2525BD%2525E7%2525A5%25259E%2525E7%2525A4%2525BE%2525E5%2525AF%2525BA%2525E5%2525BB%25259F%2525E9%252587%25258D%2525E5%252589%2525B5-%2525E6%25259C%252580%2525E5%2525B0%25259115%2525E8%252599%252595%2525E6%252596%252587%2525E7%252589%2525A9%2525E8%2525A2%2525AB%2525E6%2525AF%252580%252F&d=EK4mHTbTXwzl2O8S5iu7fp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=78506eed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhiranojinja%2Fstatus%2F1036948579489730562%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1036948579489730562%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fthestandnews.com%252Finternational%252F%2525E9%2525A3%25259B%2525E7%252587%252595%2525E8%2525A5%2525B2%2525E6%252597%2525A5-%2525E9%252597%25259C%2525E8%2525A5%2525BF%2525E4%2525BA%2525AC%2525E9%252583%2525BD%2525E7%2525A5%25259E%2525E7%2525A4%2525BE%2525E5%2525AF%2525BA%2525E5%2525BB%25259F%2525E9%252587%25258D%2525E5%252589%2525B5-%2525E6%25259C%252580%2525E5%2525B0%25259115%2525E8%252599%252595%2525E6%252596%252587%2525E7%252589%2525A9%2525E8%2525A2%2525AB%2525E6%2525AF%252580%252F&h=483932b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hiranojinja/status/1036948579489730562?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1036948579489730562&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E9%25A3%259B%25E7%2587%2595%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E9%2597%259C%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E9%2583%25BD%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25AF%25BA%25E5%25BB%259F%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2589%25B5-%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25B0%259115%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%2589%25A9%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2580%2F</a><br />\n<br />\n平野神社<br />\n@hiranojinja<br />\n 台風21号の被害が甚大なため、しばらくの間、境内の立ち入りを禁止いたします。<br />\nご迷惑をお掛け致しますが、何卒ご理解のほどよろしくお願い申し上げます。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而以千本鳥居聞名的伏見稻荷大社，就有部份圍欄被吹倒；北野天滿宮、下鴨神社等亦有不同程度災情。奈良公園亦有道路被倒塌的大樹阻擋。京都府教育委員會文化財產保護課確認，當地已有15件文物受損。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/yskond/status/1037138728471285760/photo/1?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1037138728471285760&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E9%25A3%259B%25E7%2587%2595%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E9%2597%259C%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E9%2583%25BD%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25AF%25BA%25E5%25BB%259F%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2589%25B5-%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25B0%259115%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%2589%25A9%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AF%2580%2F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyskond%2Fstatus%2F1037138728471285760%2Fphoto%2F1%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1037138728471285760%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fthestandnews.com%252Finternational%252F%2525E9%2525A3%25259B%2525E7%252587%252595%2525E8%2525A5%2525B2%2525E6%252597%2525A5-%2525E9%252597%25259C%2525E8%2525A5%2525BF%2525E4%2525BA%2525AC%2525E9%252583%2525BD%2525E7%2525A5%25259E%2525E7%2525A4%2525BE%2525E5%2525AF%2525BA%2525E5%2525BB%25259F%2525E9%252587%25258D%2525E5%252589%2525B5-%2525E6%25259C%252580%2525E5%2525B0%25259115%2525E8%252599%252595%2525E6%252596%252587%2525E7%252589%2525A9%2525E8%2525A2%2525AB%2525E6%2525AF%252580%252F&d=EK4mHTbTXwzl2O8S5iu7fp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ae81a6a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyskond%2Fstatus%2F1037138728471285760%2Fphoto%2F1%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1037138728471285760%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fthestandnews.com%252Finternational%252F%2525E9%2525A3%25259B%2525E7%252587%252595%2525E8%2525A5%2525B2%2525E6%252597%2525A5-%2525E9%252597%25259C%2525E8%2525A5%2525BF%2525E4%2525BA%2525AC%2525E9%252583%2525BD%2525E7%2525A5%25259E%2525E7%2525A4%2525BE%2525E5%2525AF%2525BA%2525E5%2525BB%25259F%2525E9%252587%25258D%2525E5%252589%2525B5-%2525E6%25259C%252580%2525E5%2525B0%25259115%2525E8%252599%252595%2525E6%252596%252587%2525E7%252589%2525A9%2525E8%2525A2%2525AB%2525E6%2525AF%252580%252F&h=fa41befb\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/yskond/status/1037138728471285760/photo/1?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1037138728471285760&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E9%25A3%259B%25E7%2587%2595%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6